cast.overview: Plagued by a violent recurring nightmare, college student Stefanie heads home to track down the one person who might be able to break the cycle and save her family from the grisly demise that inevitably awaits them all.
cast.title: Final Destination Bloodlines

details.biography:
Rya Kihlstedt (born July 23, 1970) is an American actress.

Kihlstedt was born in Lancaster, Pennsylvania and is a 1991 graduate of Skidmore College in Theatre Arts.

She is also of Swedish descent. She has two children (Ava Emanuelle born 1999, and Giovanni born 2001) with her actor husband Gil Bellows.

She is the sister of Oakland-based violinist, Carla Kihlstedt.
details.name: Rya Kihlstedt
